      "fields": {
        "summary": "Specifies CICP (Coding-independent Code Points) transfer characteristics as defined in ITU-T H.273.",
        "remarks": "<format type=\"text/markdown\"><![CDATA[\n## Remarks\n\n`SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp` enumerates the opto-electronic transfer functions defined\nby the CICP system (ITU-T H.273 / ISO 23091-2). These values are used as the\n`transferCharacteristics` parameter for\n<xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(SkiaSharp.SKColorspacePrimariesCicp,SkiaSharp.SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp)>.\n\nEach member corresponds to a numeric CICP code point. Use `Unknown` when the transfer\nfunction is not specified.\n\n## Examples\n\n```csharp\n// Create a Rec. 2020 HDR color space using PQ transfer function\nvar colorSpace = SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(\n    SKColorspacePrimariesCicp.Rec2020,\n    SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp.Pq);\n```\n]]></format>",
        "remarksRequired": true,
        "_extractedKeys": [
          "remarks",
          "summary"
        ]
      },
      "docId": null,
      "memberType": "type"
    },
